1 Okla homa Father of the Year in 2003 by the American Diabetes
2 Association; and
3 WHEREAS, Dean Blevins continues to inspire generations of
4 Oklahomans through his professionalism, integrity, and lifelong
5 dedication to his craft and his community.
6 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE 1ST SESSION
7 OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE, THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
8 CONCURRING THEREIN:
9 THAT the Oklahoma State Legislature hereby recognizes Dean
10 Blevins for his outstanding contributions to Oklahoma athletics,
11 sports journalism, and public service.
12 THAT a copy of this resolution be distributed to Dean Blevins
13 and his family as an expression of gratitude and admiration for his
14 exemplary career and legacy.
15 Adopted by the Senate the 14th day of May, 2025.
